{
    "poem_title": "Le Refus",
    "author": "Germain Nouveau",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1922",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Je suis pédéraste dans l’âme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Je le dis tout haut et debout.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Assis, je changerais de gamme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Et, couché sur un lit, Madame,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Je ne le dirais plus du tout.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je suis pédéraste dans l’âme,\nJe le dis tout haut et debout.\nAssis, je changerais de gamme,\nEt, couché sur un lit, Madame,\nJe ne le dirais plus du tout."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "La pédérastie est un vice :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "C’est l’avis de mon médecin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Je le crois, il n’est pas novice",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Quand il soutient que l’exercice",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Le plus naturel, le plus sain,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La pédérastie est un vice :\nC’est l’avis de mon médecin.\nJe le crois, il n’est pas novice\nQuand il soutient que l’exercice\nLe plus naturel, le plus sain,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Sain, comme la mer et son hâle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "L’honneur même de la maison,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Qui fait le regard le moins pâle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Le plus magnifiquement mâle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Sans aucune comparaison,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sain, comme la mer et son hâle,\nL’honneur même de la maison,\nQui fait le regard le moins pâle,\nLe plus magnifiquement mâle,\nSans aucune comparaison,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Le plus ravissant sur la terre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "C’est de froisser le traversin",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "D’une femme qu’on… désaltère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Quand elle serait adultère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Quand elle n’aurait qu’un seul sein.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le plus ravissant sur la terre,\nC’est de froisser le traversin\nD’une femme qu’on… désaltère,\nQuand elle serait adultère,\nQuand elle n’aurait qu’un seul sein."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "C’est là le sentiment intime",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "De tous les peuples sous le ciel ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Et je me fous, pour la maxime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Que l’Exception règne ou rime",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Même d’un air spirituel ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’est là le sentiment intime\nDe tous les peuples sous le ciel ;\nEt je me fous, pour la maxime,\nQue l’Exception règne ou rime\nMême d’un air spirituel ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "De tous, oui, autant que nous sommes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Aussi bien du Chinois charmant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Que du Français, peintre de pommes ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Et c’est l’opinion des hommes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Qui furent des hommes, vraiment,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "De tous, oui, autant que nous sommes,\nAussi bien du Chinois charmant\nQue du Français, peintre de pommes ;\nEt c’est l’opinion des hommes\nQui furent des hommes, vraiment,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Plus forts que ceux dont leur église",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Met les cercueils an Panthéon ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Ce sont ceux-là qu’on poétise,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Par exemple… Abraham… Moïse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Et, si tu veux… Napoléon.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Plus forts que ceux dont leur église\nMet les cercueils an Panthéon ;\nCe sont ceux-là qu’on poétise,\nPar exemple… Abraham… Moïse,\nEt, si tu veux… Napoléon."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "C’est l’opinion du plus sage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Chez les Slaves au regard clair,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Chez les Germains au doux visage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Chez les Latins au beau langage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Et chez les Bretons au cœur fier.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’est l’opinion du plus sage\nChez les Slaves au regard clair,\nChez les Germains au doux visage,\nChez les Latins au beau langage,\nEt chez les Bretons au cœur fier."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "C’est la tienne, Aimée, et la nôtre ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "C’est celle de tout bon cerveau,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Qui n’a contre elle qu’un… apôtre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Un monsieur pourtant comme un autre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Son nom ?… devra rimer en veau.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’est la tienne, Aimée, et la nôtre ;\nC’est celle de tout bon cerveau,\nQui n’a contre elle qu’un… apôtre,\nUn monsieur pourtant comme un autre,\nSon nom ?… devra rimer en veau."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "— Son nom, voyons ? — Comment, Madame",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Son nom ? mais puisqu’il n’est pas pur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Il souillerait, ce nom infâme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Tes chastes oreilles de femme ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Et puis, moi, je n’en suis pas sûr.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— Son nom, voyons ? — Comment, Madame\nSon nom ? mais puisqu’il n’est pas pur,\nIl souillerait, ce nom infâme,\nTes chastes oreilles de femme ;\nEt puis, moi, je n’en suis pas sûr."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Si c’était une calomnie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Qu’une apparence aide à courir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Je ferais une vilenie ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Son nom ? Ah ! jamais de la vie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "J’aimerais cent fois mieux mourir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si c’était une calomnie\nQu’une apparence aide à courir,\nJe ferais une vilenie ;\nSon nom ? Ah ! jamais de la vie !\nJ’aimerais cent fois mieux mourir !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "La jolie école qu’il fonde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Sans ce nom-là, pourra planer",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Dans une obscurité profonde ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "La plus belle fille du monde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Comme l’on dit, ne peut donner…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La jolie école qu’il fonde,\nSans ce nom-là, pourra planer\nDans une obscurité profonde ;\nLa plus belle fille du monde\nComme l’on dit, ne peut donner…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "D’ailleurs, Madame, cette école",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Ne fait pas beaucoup d’adhérents :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Il n’ont pas de porte-parole ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Et c’est comme une offre un peu molle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Qui rit à des indifférents.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "D’ailleurs, Madame, cette école\nNe fait pas beaucoup d’adhérents :\nIl n’ont pas de porte-parole ;\nEt c’est comme une offre un peu molle\nQui rit à des indifférents."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Cependant, sa présence agace",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Ceux qui la soupçonnent dans l’air ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Car ce soupçon va, se déplace,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Et finalement vous enlace",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Comme la vague dans la mer.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Cependant, sa présence agace\nCeux qui la soupçonnent dans l’air ;\nCar ce soupçon va, se déplace,\nEt finalement vous enlace\nComme la vague dans la mer."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Ces messieurs lisent la gazette,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Dînent en ville assez bien mis ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Quelquefois courtisent Lisette ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "J’approuve cela, mais, mazette !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Je n’en… gueule pas mes amis.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ces messieurs lisent la gazette,\nDînent en ville assez bien mis ;\nQuelquefois courtisent Lisette ;\nJ’approuve cela, mais, mazette !\nJe n’en… gueule pas mes amis."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 16,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Oui, ce vilain soupçon nous gêne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Et pourrait submerger un jour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Près de la niche, avec la chaîne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "L’Amitié, cette belle chienne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Qui hurle à sa lune d’amour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Oui, ce vilain soupçon nous gêne\nEt pourrait submerger un jour,\nPrès de la niche, avec la chaîne,\nL’Amitié, cette belle chienne,\nQui hurle à sa lune d’amour."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 17,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Pour moi, vous remarquerez comme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "J’ai quelque grâce à protester :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Passant pour la moitié d’un homme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "N’aurais-je pas le droit, en somme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "De chercher à me compléter ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour moi, vous remarquerez comme\nJ’ai quelque grâce à protester :\nPassant pour la moitié d’un homme,\nN’aurais-je pas le droit, en somme,\nDe chercher à me compléter ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 18,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "Bien mieux, tiens ! je ne suis pas large,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 87,
                    "line_text": "Mais le plus raide des paris",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
